{"tid":368470,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［心/生理學］點解有腳膠但係冇手膠？","createTime":"2017-08-21T14:33:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-21T17:26:36.000Z","uid":6436,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"67e448e8067424804efb4d0ec94538c1a0803fdc","tid":368470,"uid":6436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:33:12.000Z","msg":"男人見到啲女人著晒熱褲短裙就會好想𥄫好想奶，有啲甚至會變戀足變腳膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係兩隻手都係四肢既成員，點解地位會咁低微咁冇吸引力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好少聽有手膠手臂膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇巴絲解釋下？或者有冇啲咩學術研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9094163d8093fbaaed05cb7855f961c97d4cbaf4","tid":368470,"uid":70201,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:36:47.000Z","msg":"因為沿住對腳 大比一路望上去 就會去到絕對領域 男人生理上係有繁殖嘅慾望 所以好容易比嗰度吸引<br />\n唔知喺邊度睇過<br />\n利申 腳膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a8b38df931d6ed68fe1f931f3ccda15eb61e46d","tid":368470,"uid":55990,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:38:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"830ad0b7e387d1769868e467af8541c7d06e57a7","tid":368470,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:39:01.000Z","msg":"因為腳連住patpat<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04c816893abe51a852299151a561be17292927e6","tid":368470,"uid":55990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:39:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"37740baa052d4250405c26e4ca5f9ff8d3a2f4b4","tid":368470,"uid":3571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:39:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7f39d00aa84fab93b73c49075419e7d265d03030","tid":368470,"uid":68547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:41:25.000Z","msg":"波膠呢度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"247844322ebd578280e7277ad89501aacb25b33f","tid":368470,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:46:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為沿住對腳 大比一路望上去 就會去到絕對領域 男人生理上係有繁殖嘅慾望 所以好容易比嗰度吸引<br />\n唔知喺邊度睇過<br />\n利申 腳膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n戀足點解釋? (唔係腿)"},{"pid":"214e782a45b2dc53a1911f1e7f1b789ff58007f7","tid":368470,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:50:34.000Z","msg":"手指<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af9faaa4b44402f7113465367a0bd16cffccf910","tid":368470,"uid":53291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:55:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>因為沿住對腳 大比一路望上去 就會去到絕對領域 男人生理上係有繁殖嘅慾望 所以好容易比嗰度吸引<br />\n唔知喺邊度睇過<br />\n利申 腳膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n戀足點解釋? (唔係腿)</blockquote><br />\n好似話因爲腳唔同手或其他部位，通常都有野遮著，例如鞋<br />\n咁如果睇到腳既全部，就好似睇到私人部位咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：9up"},{"pid":"233e49e519aa9794692f2526b7d47fa1656f12f1","tid":368470,"uid":6436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T15:00:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>因為沿住對腳 大比一路望上去 就會去到絕對領域 男人生理上係有繁殖嘅慾望 所以好容易比嗰度吸引<br />\n唔知喺邊度睇過<br />\n利申 腳膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁沿住對手一路望上去, 係去到胸部, 都可以乳交啫<br />\n<br />\nbtw絕對領域 眞係好正</blockquote><br />\n我都係咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 手臂隔離就係胸，有意無意仲可以幫手夾下胸添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n胸以下就係腰，好多人都鐘意蛇腰，但係胸隔離夠有手臂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3be67d638c17ea8b1fd8f486c4a17af8b512b4d7","tid":368470,"uid":68457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T15:14:00.000Z","msg":"仲有咩膠？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"add149db3ff5d241427932caa1a0456d240716b9","tid":368470,"uid":86607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T16:02:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0396460ff4f66d042f95120582a677260fd164a0","tid":368470,"uid":93218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T16:41:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有咩膠？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n襪膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e15cd21d2fa91c5a793065775c61d1c7a230655f","tid":368470,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T16:51:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7428e702e26add62eef7b23424cf354f7d6450b8","tid":368470,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T16:54:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"638125f001c88939d335f41d13b21be9b08b2677","tid":368470,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T16:55:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"795ca59dbc4d17466b4e7b52f950edfcf8889fca","tid":368470,"uid":19638,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T16:55:54.000Z","msg":"AA膠 點算"},{"pid":"74146fa335ff4a0ae5ff8f63321784a29700fd89","tid":368470,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T17:00:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a713b54891fe9f95c2d92db991e925e2442cf556","tid":368470,"uid":61910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T17:07:06.000Z","msg":"相比起手<br />\n一般嚟講腳被包裹嘅程度會更高<br />\n<br />\n現代就話有迷你裙熱褲<br />\n但係古代<br />\n你冇可能係條街度見到女人腳<br />\n既然腳同樣充滿神秘感<br />\n咁好自然就成為性嘅投射/聯想對象<br />\n<br />\n有人話纏足其實係由足部聯想去性嘅一種體現<br />\n因為纏足嘅女人除咗改變對腳嘅形態外<br />\n仲因為咁而提高咗吸引力(如路姿、體態等<br />\n當然仲有就係對腳越包得多就越有神秘感啦<br />\n<br />\n戀足唔係現代先有<br />\n不過古人就用一D極端嘅方法去展示佢地嘅喜好咁囉"},{"pid":"f2ac0d2be5b95ffae2edb5f183f762a8d9fce7ae","tid":368470,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,